seller_description: The Raid Ant & Roach Killer is a powerful liquid solution designed to eliminate a wide variety of insects, including Cockroaches, Waterbugs, Palmetto Bugs, Ants, Silverfish, Carpet Beetles, Crickets, Earwigs, Household Spiders, Multicolored Asian Lady Beetles, Stinkbugs, Scorpions, and Black Widow Spiders. This easy-to-use spray leaves no lingering chemical odor and can be applied directly to surfaces where bugs infest, providing effective protection for your home. For continuous control, simply reapply every 4 weeks as needed. Backed by over 60 years of trusted experience, Raid delivers dependable protection for your family against household pests.
